			<ns0:name>bradc...@google.com</ns0:name><ns0:uri>/u/110304265766688778552/</ns0:uri></ns0:author><ns0:content type="html">&lt;b&gt;- Where are we today?&lt;/b&gt;
We haven't stabilized our ABI, but we have a plan coming together in the form of the &amp;quot;Integrated Runtime&amp;quot;.

&lt;b&gt;- Why is this a problem?&lt;/b&gt;
We need ABI stability before we can release a fully-enabled version of Native Client.

&lt;b&gt;- The proposed enhancement:&lt;/b&gt;
Implement the Integrated Runtime as a strategy for ABI stability.

&lt;b&gt;- Exit criteria:&lt;/b&gt;
Key stakeholders agree we have achieved ABI stability.
